<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8"
	pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
	<title>Welcome</title>
	<meta content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no' name='viewport' />
	<link rel="icon" href="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/icon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/css/custom.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/css/font.css">

</head>


<body class="index-body">
    <header class="index-header">
        <ul class="indexheader-inner">
            
            <li class="indexlogo-inner">
                <div class="index-logo">
                    <img src="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/bpms_logo.svg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="index-title no-drag">
                    <span>Best</span>
                    <span>P</span>
                    <span>M</span>
                    <span>S</span>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li class="indexlogo-signup">
                <a href="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/login/loginForm.do" class="signupbtn">
                    시작하기
                </a>
            </li>
            
        </ul>
    </header>
    
    <section class="index-section">
        <div class="indexsection-inner">
            <div class="indexsection-header">
                <img src="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/index/Website Hosting.svg" alt="">
                <img src="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/index/cloud.png" alt="">
                <ul class="indextitle-inner">
                    <li class="indexright-title">
                        <span>
                            웹을 통해<br>
                            프로젝트를 효율적으로<br>
                            관리하세요
                        </span>
                        <a href="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/login/loginForm.do" class="indexstart-button">
                            무료로 시작
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <caption class="indexcontent-title">
        <span class="indexcontent-title">
            <h2>편의 기능 제공</h2>
            <span>
                캘린더, 커밋 히스토리, 문서 보관함, 대시보드, 프로젝트 채팅 등<br>
                편리한 도구와 함께 사용하세요.
            </span>
        </span>
        <ul class="indexcontent-inner">
            <li>
                <img src="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/index/calendar.png" alt="">
                <span class="indexfunction-intoroduce">
                    <h2>캘린더</h2>
                    <span>
                        일감, 이슈 및 일정을 달력에 추가하고
                        조정해 팀원들과 공유하세요.
                    </span>
                </span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="indexfunction-intoroduce">
                    <h2>SCM</h2>
                    <span>
                        프로젝트 관리 도구(SVN, GIT) 커밋 내역을
                        웹으로 조회하세요.
                    </span>
                </span>
                <img src="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/index/SCM.png" alt="">
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/index/file.png" alt="">
                <span class="indexfunction-intoroduce">
                    <h2>프로젝트 문서함</h2>
                    <span>
                        프로젝트내 첨부된 모든 문서를 조회하고
                        선택해 다운로드 하세요.
                    </span>
                </span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="indexfunction-intoroduce">
                    <h2>관리자/프로젝트 대시보드</h2>
                    <span>
                        프로젝트 진행 상황을 한 눈에 파악할 수 있는
                        대시보드를 제공합니다.
                    </span>
                </span>
                <img src="${pageContext.request.contextPath }/assets/img/index/admin.png" alt="">
            </li>
        </ul>
    </caption>

    <footer class="index-footer">
        <div class="indexfooter-inner">
            Copyright © 2021 Deadock Team 1
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>